 of Noah, and from it hail draperies and fine rugs of lots of peculiarities the filament of which is like that of Dwin, and of its towns are: [a list of settlements follows]."}]},{"pos":"name","gloss":"Khoy County (a county of West Azerbaijan Province, Iran) (مُقَاطَعَة خُوَيّ (muqāṭaʕa ḵuwayy))"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/xa.wi.ja/","/xu.wajj/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11782","headword_ar":"خَوًى","root":"xwY","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Emptiness of the belly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K;) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its emptiness of food;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xawaA='N","text_ar":"خَوَا=ءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) [both inf. ns.;] the former of higher authority than the latter. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hunger;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xawaA='N","text_ar":"خَوَا=ءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaw~N","text_ar":"خَوٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA. [In the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wAlxuw~u bAlD~am~i AlEasalu","text_ar":"والخُوُّ بالضَّمِّ العَسَلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wAlxaw~u wabiAlD~am~i AlEasalu","text_ar":"والخَوُّ وَبِالضَّمِّ العَسَلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". The word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaw~N","text_ar":"خَوٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"belongs to art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xw","text_ar":"خو"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xawaA='N","text_ar":"خَوَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  Also, ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxawiY~N","text_ar":"الخَوِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the CK being a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxawaY","text_ar":"الخَوَى"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"page_break","n":828},{